{
  "stem": "6195.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we had the passes because my uncle, who owned a factory before the war-- factories and businesses were taken over by so-called German [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my uncle made a deal with a German [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He says you can have the factory.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You can have everything you want.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'll give you some money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't care what you do with the factory, whether you run it, you burn it, or whatever, but I want from you passes from the ghetto-- this was this uncle that I have shown to you, the girl, my cousin-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] for my family passes.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And let us that they work in that factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And for himself, but then he had, I think, Argentinian passport, and stayed outside the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because if you had a foreign passport, not a Polish one, even though you were Jewish, you were allowed to live outside the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that's how we could get out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And how I kept getting some money is I-- each time I took some linen, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] whatever I had, curtains that I took off from-- not from all the rooms, but from two rooms-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] so each time I went to Cracow, I sold something.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And when I sold it-- it may seem very peculiar-- I suddenly became enterprising.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I bought some sausage, and I bought butter, but that was already later.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was summer.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was very hot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I put the butter underneath here and kept it with the belt and the sausage.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Not too much of it, but I thought I'll sell one and, and keep one for us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Well, you won't believe me.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
